<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هوَى٢ يَهوِي، اهْوِ، هَوِيًّا وهَوَاءً، فهو هاوٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• هوَى الشَّخصُ:</span> هلَك.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• هوَتِ المرأةُ:</span> فقدت ولدَها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>